{"tid":124192,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲有睇Peaceful Cuisine 個Youtube Channel","createTime":"2017-02-17T11:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T07:39:41.000Z","uid":77205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a09f8e8dee36e96795e21ac0bfbd90246856730","tid":124192,"uid":77205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"因為Bob叔最近好似慢左出片, 所以之前連登有巴打開post問有冇Youtube Channel 可以睇住先頂下癮先<br />\n除左Bob 叔自己都推薦過嘅Channel &quot;Food Wishes&quot;(Chef John) 同 &quot;Bruno Albouze&quot;之外, 小弟仲想推介下呢個由日本仔開嘅Youtube Channel 叫 &quot;Peaceful Cuisine&quot; 佢嘅特色係<br />\n1. 部分影片係冇背景音樂嘅, 淨係得煮食物嘅聲音(eg 斬瓜切菜嘅聲), 好治癒, 最近網上流傳嗰條片'無音樂整朱古力蛋糕'條片都係佢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 佢set gear真係好好J , 入過去水吧冲啡嘅巴打可以留意吓佢用呢出shot嗰部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該係我ㄧ年人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 佢好多野食都可以用自己屋企set gear整, 咁畢竟唔係個個屋企都有BBQ架可以整煙燻牛肉或咁大個焗爐整啤酒雞嫁麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (講下笑咋Bob叔, 有怪莫怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n最後: Bob 叔我地等你d片呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日你又有話題可以講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c521b414fdcaa4c303916afd5016187db4d5d64c","tid":124192,"uid":77205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T15:43:59.000Z","msg":"輕輕ㄧ推<br />\n仲有而且佢d 材料都係fair trade/ 標榜organic/ 自己種"},{"pid":"c5d726696174bd91e545671c2f324b28e0188efd","tid":124192,"uid":56909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T15:46:37.000Z","msg":"佢個廚房好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有野都執得好整齊，分哂類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一諗起自己冇可能有間咁靚既屋就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"